                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18091101-113-defend890 t18091101-113-punish704"></join>
               at the expiration of that time to find sureties for her good behaviour for six months
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>London jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
